i style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;break-inside:avoid\"><span style=\"font-family:BookSanity\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.03em\">Component Cost:</strong> 200 gp</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;break-inside:avoid\"><span style=\"font-family:BookSanity\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.03em\">Ingredients:</strong> (Snake Venom | Spider Venom | Scorpion Venom)</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;break-inside:avoid\"><span style=\"font-family:BookSanity\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.03em\">Extract DC:</strong> 11           <strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.03em\">Recipe DC:</strong> 13</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;break-inside:avoid\"><span style=\"font-family:BookSanity\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.03em\">Poison DC:</strong> 12, Constitution saving throw</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;break-inside:avoid\"><span style=\"font-family:BookSanity\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.03em\">Effect:</strong> You can apply this poison to one slashing or piercing weapon, or on up to three pieces of ammunition. A creature hit by the poisoned weapon must make a DC 12 Constitution saving throw, taking 1d4 + modifier poison damage on a fail, or half as much damage on a successful save.</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;break-inside:avoid\"><span style=\"font-family:BookSanity\"><strong styl